text: You can take the lift that is located just outside Koufu to access this rooftop garden. It is located at level 5, on top of a multistory carpark. The view is not great but you can see the Commomwealth MRT station and the Tanglin Halt neighbourhood. There were not many flowers but the place was clean and spacious. There were also some exercise equipment.
It is amazing that a rooftop garden has so many mature and shady trees. Looks even better than a lot of on-ground gardens.
very big roof garden with playground
